com.checkout.android_sdk.Store

Class DataStore

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.checkout.android_sdk.Store.DataStore

  • public class DataStore
extends java.lang.Object
    The DataStore

    Used to contain state within the SDK for easy communication between custom components. It is also used preserve and restore state when in case the device orientation changes.
